         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the god Asklepios <supplied reason="subaudible">in payment of</supplied> a <rs type="subject">vow</rs>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Dedication of a promised object (not described) by an unnamed dedicator, doubtless in gratitude for a cure. The object dedicated may well have been an image of the part of the body that had been cured.</p>
         </div>
